<p class="center">Per Governor Abbot, school is closed this schol year.</p><br><p class="center">All New Home ISD facilities will be CLOSED until further notice.</p><br><p class="center">All school related activities will be POSTPONED until further notice.</p><br><p class="center">If you qualify for free or reduced meals and would like to continue to receive meals please contact Brady Webb at <a href="mailto:bwebb@esc17.net">bwebb@esc17.net</a> or call 806-924-7543 ext 208. Meals will be available beginning March 30.</p><br><p class="center">For support with Google Classroom and other IT areas, contact Shane Moore at <a href="mailto:helpdesk@newhomeisd.net">helpdesk@newhomeisd.net</a></p><br>
